        "color_scheme_2": "background-1",
        "heading": "<p>Jennifer Sey</p>",
        "subheading": "<p><strong>Founder &amp; CEO<br><br></strong>I am very grateful for your support. The creation of this brand is the culmination of everything I’ve ever done in my life:my athletic background as an elite gymnast; standing up for athletes to expose the abuses in my beloved sport; 30 years in corporate America, which ended with me leading one of the most famous clothing brands in the world; and then really ended with me getting cancelled for standing up for kids. <br><br>I believe in getting up when you get knocked down (sports taught me that). I believe in comebacks, big ideas and the magic of teams with diverse points of view. That led me to create a whole new brand. One that is my own. <br> <br>If you believe in truth, free speech and open debate, and challenging the patently false and deeply entrenched narratives of the day, this is the brand for you!<br> <br>It can be scary to stand up and stand apart to speak the truth. But if we do it together . . . it’s a little less scary. So, wear your XX-XY Athletics gear with pride. Help us save women's sports and keep women's spaces safe. <br><br><strong>The truth looks good on you.</strong><br> <br>-Jen</p>",
